public class MainForm
extends javax.swing.JFrame

This class actually generates the graphical user interface (GUI). The GUI simplifies generation of realistic simulation environments for OMNeT++. Such an environment includes hierarchical topologies, background traffic and special node types, e.g. DDoSZombie that generates DDoS attacks.

1.0-developer version
